    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "but its not like construction or an appliance... those things have a pattern or stop at night. this is different. it feels targeted. like it's specifically tuned to a frequency that just... messes with my head. i've been reading about infrasound and how it can cause paranoia and physical discomfort. do you think it's actually possible for someone to use that kind of tech in a normal apartment building? like, on purpose?",
