      "content": "Infrasound, which are very low-frequency sound waves, can indeed cause physical sensations like unease, anxiety, and even feelings of pressure in the body. It is theoretically possible to generate these kinds of frequencies, and some experimental or niche applications have been discussed regarding its effects on humans. Since this feels targeted, documenting the exact times and feelings is important for a clearer picture. If you suspect deliberate harassment, you may need to consult local authorities or an expert to investigate the source.",
